HEADWORD: hawks-beard
<hw>hawk's-beard</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>Any of various plants of the
genus <gen>Crepis</gen> having loose heads of yellow flowers on top of a
long branched leafy stem; found in the Northern hemisphere.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> hawk's-beards.</syn>⟦br⟧
